{"tid":703312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「中國成最大贏家」？美媒被爆收北京錢寫新聞","createTime":"2018-06-15T15:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-15T16:18:33.000Z","uid":39464,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5d31061595e4cb46572b16a30b19616acd830493","tid":703312,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180615/640_e5426e9da92bf59f17c71f86f1c84c06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180615%2F640_e5426e9da92bf59f17c71f86f1c84c06.jpg&h=72e327cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國知名新聞網站Vox，被爆收取北京政府支持的組織資金，撰寫軟性新聞文章。<br />\n最近Vox外電編輯Yochi Dreazen發表一篇新聞，標題為「川金會的最大贏家？中國」（The big winner of the Trump-Kim summit？China）。但仔細一看，在文章底部，特別註明了它是由「中美交流基金會」所資助。<br />\n文章底部寫下註解：「本篇報導是由中美交流基金會（CUSEF）資助，這是一間總部在香港的私人資助非營利機構，致力於『促使中美兩國的政策制定者、商界領袖、學者、智庫、文化界及教育工作者，進行開放且有建設性的交流』。」這個介紹跟中美交流基金會網站的英文介紹用語如出一轍。<br />\n「中美交流基金會」是中國政府支持的組織，在海外宣傳中國。這則「置入新聞」率先由《華爾街日報》專欄作家Josh Rogin發現。Rogin在推特上質問Vox：「你知道CUSEF由中國共產黨內具影響力的一名高級官員當主席，對吧？他就是董建華，CUSEF的主席是中國全國政協副主席，（全國政協）與在海外推動黨目標的統戰部有關。」<br />\n目前美國國會議員致力打擊，中國利用美國媒體作為政治宣傳，也因此Vox跟中美交流基金會的關係備受關注。美國參議院2018年度國防授權法案中，特別提到「中國正透過影響美國媒體、文化機構、商家、學術和政策社群，對自身安全、軍事政策等目標更加有利」。近月，中美交流基金會也因為被指滲透德州大學奧斯汀分校，被美國國會所盯上。（北美中心 ／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180615/640_9283bf27a8f456dbeaf846f05fc54586.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180615%2F640_9283bf27a8f456dbeaf846f05fc54586.jpg&h=69c40a6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n文章底部註明了是由中美交流基金會贊助。翻攝Vox網站<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180615/1374017/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180615%2F1374017%2F&d=j%2BGigg9e8pTkALk91wtY6%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=7960aaad\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180615%2F1374017%2F&h=5423f2ef\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180615/1374017/</a>"},{"pid":"c6141c969a76d6daf158f121e93818a4bb40373b","tid":703312,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:40:44.000Z","msg":"實捉到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47f12f0465de64a6cd6a53aba511a6639fc69890","tid":703312,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:42:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d652d7e7327ead17986603907406089fb2ec82b","tid":703312,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e333ddbb0ae95949a857241c3799ee092cf3b85d","tid":703312,"uid":83015,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:51:28.000Z","msg":"你知道CUSEF由中國共產黨內具影響力的一名高級官員當主席，對吧？他就是<span style=\"color: red;\">董建華</span>，CUSEF的主席是中國全國政協副主席，（全國政協）與在海外推動黨目標的統戰部有關"},{"pid":"f0c870e6a55af3e92cb9b8c8d26828be9ffc9349","tid":703312,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:52:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6301f873db94718422431cb932f4544ce095f55b","tid":703312,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:52:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e93cb3a8726b7a1a4c6cb9efe8665fc6a64e8cd","tid":703312,"uid":36441,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-15T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"姐係話親中國係贏家就收左錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d21b00e3e0dd486c1aae415e14e4ca7b21976685","tid":703312,"uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci